Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:03.95,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Summer means vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.18,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Vacations are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:10.92,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do radio calisthenics every morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,eat hiyamugi noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and eat shaved ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll swim in the pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:16.55,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,eat cold ramen noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:18.41,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and eat ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.49,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:23.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I am Gouda Takeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,a first-year in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.92,SignA,Sign 0025,0000,0000,0000,,Report Card
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In its own way, it's awe-inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.93,Phone,Sign 0035,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:41.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was just talking with my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:44.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,about how it'd be great if we all went \Nto the beach with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.38,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun... Invite Sunakawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:49.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Would Sunakawa-kun come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:51.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The beach sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.50,SignB,Sign 0224,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,521)}My Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:24.01,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.35,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the beach with Takeo's \Ngirlfriend and her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.58,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.20,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.01,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:29.75,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:31.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.68,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's wide and vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.13,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you're coming, \Nwhether you want to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:39.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.18,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so looking forward to seeing girls in swimsuits...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:43.65,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:44.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:45.81,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:50.06,SignC,Sign 0248,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations {\c&H16181E&}                          Big Catch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Swimsuits are for swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:50.99,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.20,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.19,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to a beach, it's all about watching \Ngirls in swimsuits, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.04,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:58.49,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you looking forward to seeing \Nyour girlfriend in a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato's coming in a swimsuit just to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:06.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never turn into a scumbag \Nthat'd stare at her like a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It won't matter to me what you wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.81,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Which one are you gonna choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.00,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky! You have a big rack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.84,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,You have nice legs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.27,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,You have a nice figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.88,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.73,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.47,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,A high-cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess that's too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then... Maybe this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.23,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But I mean, Takeo-kun's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.09,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.51,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.11,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0345,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(167,217)}Of course he is to Rinko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to him, I'm like a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.87,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0348,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(192,1)}I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a good figure like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.56,Default - italics,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure you'd call him "hot."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.28,Default - italics,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, he isn't built like a \Nnormal high school first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.77,Default - italics,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,He has ridiculous muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.88,Default - italics,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a heavy weightlifter in the Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:02.38,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what your boyfriend's going to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.32,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,What if he brings a school swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.06,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Totally possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.27,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,What if it's like the competitive kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.73,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,The really tiny ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.39,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he'll swim a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:15.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:19.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He always makes my heart skip a beat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to make his heart skip a beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.53,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0423,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(114,1)}I'm going to give it my best shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.67,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.97,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.05,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you want your boyfriend's \Nheart to skip a beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.91,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,You want him to think you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:34.04,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's help Rinko pick out her swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.29,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.60,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,This one's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.31,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:38.99,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.94,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Those bottom frills are definitely gonna turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:41.80,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.92,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're already in here, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you running away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was packing up for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:08.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go over what I have, \Nto avoid doubling up on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have enough canteens to cook \Nrice, and tents for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to the beach to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that we'll get stranded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to lose by \Npreparing for a rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there'll be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:22.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takeo-kun? They're forecasting a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll be okay tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You always bring good weather \Nwith you, so it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna says we don't need to worry, \Nbecause I bring good weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:39.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at Suna's place getting ready for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:52.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:56.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Watermelons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing the watermelon game, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that a bit much? \NHow many did you pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Also, shouldn't you wait till we get there \Nto inflate the floats and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It takes up too much space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, are you really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.85,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.84,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I saw the sun set into the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:27.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and it blew me away.
