Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:43.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But he's always one step ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:47.00,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,You really like your boyfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.44,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go snuggle up to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.47,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko would die first from excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.20,SFX-BlueBlue,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(83,1)\c&H16181E&\fs20}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.63,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You sure eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:31.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can the two of us go to the rocks over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.14,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,The rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.87,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You want to catch small crabs. Right, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:44.13,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super good at catching crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.89,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:57.60,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:01.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'll step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:10.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.64,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:48.32,SignE,Sign 1648,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(272,1)\an9}This is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:50.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was just so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:24.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You keep an eye out on what's \Ngoing on around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I was too focused on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so self-centered...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bad today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:45.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.65,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right... I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:12.23,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see this sunset with Yamato today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.59,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we're doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a happy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:33.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a person with \Na mind as open as the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:39.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And stay with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:41.26,SignE,Sign 1840,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko             Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.06,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.06,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.32,SignE,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko             Takeo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of the sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.77,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why my face is burning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.27,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,and my heart's pounding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:39.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I love you lots, too, Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.72,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:51.79,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1950,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(898,1)}ba-dum ba-dum
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.71,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.61,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.46,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:02.71,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.05,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do fireworks! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.75,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.06,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:18.03,Default,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you didn't manage to make \Nhis heart skip a beat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.42,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,And you tried so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But it was still fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.70,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.99,Default,Ayu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should all go see \Nfireworks and stuff together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.20,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,And wear yukatas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.26,Default,Kojima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yukatas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:40.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can make Takeo-kun's \Nheart skip a beat with a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.47,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 2040,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko, you don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:47.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I was blown away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,when I watched the sunset with Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime, do you want to go to a \Nfireworks festival with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:07.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.81,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Takeo-kun's heart skip a beat for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.65,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato and fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll get blown away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like fireworks, Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:24.48,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,These two really aren't on the same page.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.12,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.49,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They sure look happy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.98,SignF,Sign 2135,0000,0000,0000,,Rinko             Takeo
